{"title":"公社新人","authors":["李晓白"],"dates":[{"year":1960,"month":6,"day":8}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"公社新人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"李晓白"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"农业专家就"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就在这块土地上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"地主剥走他的破棉袄；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"经受着饥饿和鞭打，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"泪珠不知流过多少；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"骨头被担子压弯了！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"胡子被风霜染白了！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就在这块土地上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把幸福的日子迎来了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"昨天装上电动水车，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天拖拉机又来报到；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"宁让敬老院的椅子空着，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他要向土地把债讨。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就在这块土地上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他用心血把生活灌浇；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把豆子嫁接在南瓜蔓上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"椿树上结下了棉桃……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他摸熟了泥土的性格，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沿着总路线走上灿烂的大道。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就在这块土地上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敲锣打鼓彩旗飘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千百名代表、大学生，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来听专家的报告，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"书记扶着他走上讲台，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他流着眼泪不住地笑。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山村老大娘"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"苍发飘飘汗珠淌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"割完了麦子洒好了场，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"笑看麦堆步步高，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心儿在算丰收账，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"提着镰刀往回走，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"后边有人喊大娘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“队长呀，三缺一，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打打扑克乘乘凉。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大娘笑着回头说："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“没工夫呵请原谅；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"报社昨天打电话，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要我写篇小文章。”"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}